18.description:
Soukboard is an online sales and marketing assistant for small and medium businesses. 
Sales performance is the goal. At Soukboard, small and medium businesses owners can create their own online stores, promote their products through intelligent online marketing campaigns and grow their sales; everything in a single platform and paying only per conversion, 

Soukboard offers SMB what no other online store platform does:
* A FREE online store, with strong focus on UX design.
* Integrated simplified online campaigns tools (google ads, facebook ads among others) inside each store,
* A smart algorithm that learns from all the campaigns performed at the Soukboard community and optimizes each stores’ campaigns
* A dashboard with statistics that enables anyone to manage their campaigns and make decisions.

Soukboard is a self-service platform, as users can register, login, create their stores, sale their products and use the integrated online marketing tools by themselves. The smart assistant is completely automatized based on each stores information, sales profile, etc.
